      "content": "i've already talked to my doctors. they just keep adjusting things and it never actually works. it’s just different types of useless. it feels like i'm just trapped in a body that's broken, and there's no light at the end of this. honestly, sometimes it feels like the only way to actually get some peace is to just... not be here anymore. does that sound crazy?",
